#: src-en/data/events_special_morality.xml.append:131
msgid ""
"data/events_special_morality.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MORALITY_REMOVE_GENERAL_DOUBLE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"[恶名减少 X2- 整体]\n"
"\t你为整个银河系做了一件好事。若你在过去的其他行为中获得了恶名，那么更有可能因现在的行为而被原谅。\n"
"\t由于你的额外英勇之举，你的恶名被降低了两级。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_morality.xml.append:138
msgid ""
"data/events_special_morality.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REPUTATION_UPDATE_SLAVER_MEMBERSHIP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"[声望提升 x10 - 奴隶贩子]\n"
